FBIS3-35944 "drsov021__a94006" FBIS-SOV-94-021-A Document Type:Daily Report 1 February 1994 ANNEX Russia National Affairs Yeltsin Signs Instruction Appointing Two Officials LD2701114494 Moscow RIA in English 0938 GMT 27 Jan 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY LD2701114494 Moscow RIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow, January 27, RIA--President Boris Yeltsin has signed an instruction on appointing Gen. Dmitriy Volkogonov as chief of a presidential commission to investigate cases of missing foreigners and Russian citizens missing elsewhere. The president has also signed an instruction on appointing Yekaterina Lakhova as chief of a presidential commission for female, family and demographic affairs, reports the presidential press service.
